    "description": "Embark on an epic fantasy adventure in SideQuest Hunters, an innovative Idle RPG Roguelite that plays<strong> in the corner of your screen</strong>. Designed for those who enjoy constant progression and wealth accumulation, this game allows you to venture into a magical world without interrupting your other activities.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209700/extras/7b37a4cb7ed390222355c513b486c983.poster.avif?t=1744736430\" width=616 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209700/extras/7b37a4cb7ed390222355c513b486c983.webm?t=1744736430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209700/extras/7b37a4cb7ed390222355c513b486c983.mp4?t=1744736430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><br>- <strong> Multitasking</strong>: Enjoy the thrill of an RPG without having to dedicate long hours. Ideal for playing while doing other tasks in front of your computer.<br><br>- b]Hunt them all[/b]:Advance through the different areas defeating all kinds of enemies. Complete your record of monsters to be the best hunter.<br><br>- <strong>Sublime pixel art</strong>: Enjoy throughout your adventure amazing characters and environments with fantastic pixel-art by the great Rafael Matos.<br><br>- b]Automatic Battles[/b]: Engage in strategic battles that unfold automatically, allowing you to concentrate on managing and progressing your heroes.<br><br>- <strong>Infinity of items</strong>: Discover and purchase different items that will make every game feel unique. Build the perfect build to go where no one else has gone before.<br><br>- b]Continuous Progression[/b]: Close the game at any time and pick up your adventure where you left off.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209700/extras/994497967e1fcc5f7e1ff5b54cd53301.poster.avif?t=1744736430\" width=616 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209700/extras/994497967e1fcc5f7e1ff5b54cd53301.webm?t=1744736430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209700/extras/994497967e1fcc5f7e1ff5b54cd53301.mp4?t=1744736430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UPCOMING UPDATES</h2>.<br>- <strong>New hunters</strong>: New hunters will arrive, with unique mechanics, attributes and items. <br><br>- <strong>New areas and enemies</strong>: New zones full of unique enemies, which will add variety and hours of gameplay.<br><br>- b]New features and tweaks[/b]: We will listen to the community to bring you the best possible gameplay experience.<br><br><br><br>Get ready to explore, fight and progress in SideQuest Hunters, where the adventure never stops.<br><br><br>Thank you for playing SideQuest Hunters, we hope it will accompany you during the long hours in front of your computer.<br><br>Fdo: CanoCoder &amp; MorenoGameDev<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209700/extras/2658c7e146b6279d2aa99e2fa7c1bfaa.poster.avif?t=1744736430\" width=256 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209700/extras/2658c7e146b6279d2aa99e2fa7c1bfaa.webm?t=1744736430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209700/extras/2658c7e146b6279d2aa99e2fa7c1bfaa.mp4?t=1744736430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
